 Fertilizer  The directive should be seen what it is: a wakeup call for self-sufficiency in food production. It is a challenge to investors who would like to take to agriculture business. We would also like to add that the president should ensure that there is an enabling environment too for agriculture to thrive. There should be robust investment and commitment to rural electrification schemes and good rural road projects, among other needs of agriculture businessmen.  To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .